reviews.text:
Back in the day my friends and I would chow down on those dissolving dishwasher tablets. It wasn't until later in life we realized how much better a liquid based detergent could taste. &#xD;
This recipe brings me back to the first time we tried Tide's pods. The difference was astounding, as if my whole life had been a lie up to that point. Why bother with something that dissolves in your mouth when it can burst with flavor? It's like going from sweet tart double lollies to gushers. &#xD;
It truly cleansed my soul and vaping this recipe had similar, longstanding, effects. Like a primal awakening or an ascension.&#xD;
Truly, this recipe showcases a mastery of flavor profiles and culinary discipline. I can't recommend it enough.&#xD;
**You have not lived until you've experienced this recipe.**
